In England, in the seven days to 05 August, there were 165,055 new confirmed cases (291.9 new cases per 100,000). There is no change in cases compared to those confirmed in the previous week (seven days to 29 July). The number of confirmed COVID-19 cases in England so far as at 10 August is 5,344,609 (9,451.1 cases per 100,000 population).
